er Erzählungen lesenswerte neue Sichtweisen auf Integration und Integrationskurse sowie auf Sprache, Bildung und Urbanität bietet.  afunded by Universität Innsbruck  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 4aBildung. 4aBildungssoziologie. 4aBrüssel. 4aDiversität. 4aGesellschaft. 4aIntegration. 4aKulturkonflikt. 4aKultursoziologie. 4aMigration. 4aPostmigrantische Gesellschaft. 4aQualitative Sozialforschung. 4aRuhrgebiet. 4aSoziologie. 4aSprache. 4aUrbanität. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Emigration & Immigration.2bisacsh  aBrussels.  aCulture Conflict.  aDiversity.  aEducation.  aIntegration.  aLanguage.  aMigration.  aPost-migrant Society.  aQualitative Social Research.  aRuhr Area.  aSociety.  aSociology of Culture.  aSociology of Education.  aSociology.  aUrbanity.2 aUniversität Innsbruckefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology 2021z9783110753967oZDB-23-DSL0 cprintz978383765727240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839457276?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839457276423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839457276/original  a978-3-11-074335-7  DG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2b2021  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2021  aZDB-23-DSLb2021